Package: tayloR
Type: Package
Title: Taylor Series Expansion
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Im-a-scRiptR
Description: This package performs the Taylor Series Expansion for any given 
  single variable function. It also includes a remainder calculation function
  as well as the Taylor Remainder plot.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    magrittr,
    stats,
    stringr,
    tibble
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0.0)
BugReports: https://github.com/Im-a-scRiptR/tayloR/issues
URL: https://github.com/Im-a-scRiptR/tayloR
